Package: nycOpenData
Type: Package
Title: Easy Access to NYC Open Data APIs
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Christian", "Martinez", 
           email = "c.martinez0@outlook.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains functions that allow for pulling of different NYC Open Data 
    datasets from <https://opendata.cityofnewyork.us/>. The initial release includes 
    the 'nyc_311()' function for retrieving 311 Service Request data in a tidy format.
